I better finish the first one.

00:17:28.200 --> 00:17:28.866
DAN STONE: Yeah.

00:17:29.550 --> 00:17:30.550
Finish up the first one.

00:17:30.550 --> 00:17:32.160
DANIEL HANDLER: This is where
you get in trouble, I always

00:17:32.160 --> 00:17:34.290
think, in drinking, is
when someone's like, hey,

00:17:34.290 --> 00:17:34.925
you ready for another one?

00:17:34.925 --> 00:17:35.760
And you're not.

