But house bacon infused
Four Roses bourbon.

00:18:06.980 --> 00:18:09.520
So I went to Berkeley
Bowl yesterday,

00:18:09.520 --> 00:18:14.310
and they dragged a pig out from
the back of the butcher shop,

00:18:14.310 --> 00:18:16.150
and carved three pounds of fat.

00:18:16.150 --> 00:18:17.358
DANIEL HANDLER: Already dead.

00:18:17.358 --> 00:18:18.516
The pig was already dead.

00:18:18.516 --> 00:18:19.970
DAN STONE: Yeah,
the pig was dead.

00:18:19.970 --> 00:18:21.386
DANIEL HANDLER: I
had this fantasy

00:18:21.386 --> 00:18:25.500
about how the customers
of Berkeley Bowl

00:18:25.500 --> 00:18:27.830
would take to a pig being
slaughtered in the store,

00:18:27.830 --> 00:18:28.660
