00:32:06.511 --> 00:32:07.020
It's great.

00:32:07.020 --> 00:32:07.810
DAN STONE: Yeah.

00:32:07.810 --> 00:32:08.310
Yeah.

00:32:08.310 --> 00:32:09.030
It is good.

00:32:10.057 --> 00:32:10.890
[INTERPOSING VOICES]

00:32:12.605 --> 00:32:14.730
DANIEL HANDLER: You know
