00:32:41.225 --> 00:32:42.600
DANIEL HANDLER:
Because we talked

00:32:42.600 --> 00:32:45.270
about a book that I love, and
a poem that I love, and then

00:32:45.270 --> 00:32:46.390
we're going to show
