It reminds me of Elizabeth
Berkeley in "Showgirls."

00:36:40.790 --> 00:36:41.290
Distinctly.

00:36:41.290 --> 00:36:42.125
DAN STONE: Touche.

00:36:42.125 --> 00:36:43.000
DANIEL HANDLER: Yeah.

