I mean, I found her to
not be a terrible actress

00:36:45.849 --> 00:36:47.890
to carry this movie, just
because the movie is so

00:36:47.890 --> 00:36:49.470
over the top.

00:36:49.470 --> 00:36:51.050
Just so melodramatic.

00:36:51.050 --> 00:36:55.765
Just unapologetically excessive.

00:36:56.539 --> 00:36:57.205
DAN STONE: Yeah.

00:36:57.205 --> 00:36:58.370
DANIEL HANDLER: And
there's poetry in it.

00:36:58.370 --> 00:36:59.940
I find it very
beautiful, this movie.

00:36:59.940 --> 00:37:01.590
I mean, it's
ridiculous, but when

00:37:01.590 --> 00:37:03.500
you get past it
being ridiculous,

00:37:03.500 --> 00:37:05.420
and you get all the way
all around the circle,

00:37:05.420 --> 00:37:06.617
it starts to makes sense to.

